body_html: This looks like some sort of mismatch between the protobuf used by onnx and Caffe2. Have you built ONNX separately? What is the full cmake output? If you built ONNX from source, can you make sure to pass PROTOBUF_INCDIR=/path/to/protobuf/used/to/build/caffe2 ?

body: This looks like some sort of mismatch between the protobuf used by onnx and Caffe2. Have you built ONNX separately? What is the full cmake output? If you built ONNX from source, can you make sure to pass PROTOBUF_INCDIR=/path/to/protobuf/used/to/build/caffe2 ?
